OL,3,CJustin Welby says he forgives abuser
OL,4,CSmyth and tells of 'personal failure'
OL,6,FFormer archbishop of Canterbury Justin
OL,7,FWelby said he forgives serial abuser
OL,8,FJohn Smyth as he repeated an apology
OL,9,Fto victims and told of the "deep sense
OL,10,Fof personal failure" he feels about
OL,11,Fthe handling of allegations.
OL,13,FThe former most senior bishop in the
OL,14,FChurch of England, who resigned in
OL,15,FNovember and stepped down officially
OL,16,Fin January, said he had "not really
OL,17,Fthought it through enough, to be
OL,18,Fhonest" when he initially declined to
OL,19,Fquit last year.
