OL,3,CJustin Welby says he forgives abuser
OL,4,CSmyth and tells of 'personal failure'
OL,6,FThe Makin report into Smyth ` thought
OL,7,Fto be the most prolific abuser
OL,8,Fassociated with the Church ` concluded
OL,9,FMr Welby did not adequately follow up
OL,10,Fon reports about the Christian camp
OL,11,Fleader and barrister.
OL,13,FIt said Smyth might have been brought
OL,14,Fto justice had Mr Welby formally
OL,15,Freported allegations to police in 2013.
OL,17,FMr Welby initially said he would not
OL,18,Fresign over the report and remained in
OL,19,Fpost for a further five days before
OL,20,Fannouncing he would quit.
