OL,3,CJustin Welby says he forgives abuser
OL,4,CSmyth and tells of 'personal failure'
OL,6,FIn his first interview since his
OL,7,Fresignation, he told the BBC's Sunday
OL,8,FWith Laura Kuenssberg programme: "What
OL,9,Fchanged my mind was having been caught
OL,10,Fby the report being leaked and not
OL,11,Freally thought it through enough, to
OL,12,Fbe honest.
OL,14,F"Over that weekend, as I read it and
OL,15,Freread it and as I reflected on the
OL,16,Fhorrible suffering of the survivors
OL,17,Fwhich had been, as many of them said,
OL,18,Fmore than doubled by the institutional
OL,19,FChurch's failure to respond
OL,20,Fadequately, it increasingly became
OL,21,Fclear to me that I needed to resign."
