OL,3,CJustin Welby says he forgives abuser
OL,4,CSmyth and tells of 'personal failure'
OL,6,FElsewhere in the interview, he
OL,7,Findicated he forgives Smyth, who is
OL,8,Fsaid to have subjected as many as 130
OL,9,Fboys and young men to traumatic abuse
OL,10,Facross five decades in three different
OL,11,Fcountries in the UK and Africa.
OL,13,F"Yes, I think if he was alive and I
OL,14,Fsaw him," he said when asked if he
OL,15,Fforgives the now dead clergyman.
OL,17,F"But it's not, it's not me he has
OL,18,Fabused. He's abused the victims and
OL,19,Fsurvivors. So, whether I forgive or
OL,20,Fnot is, to a large extent, irrelevant."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@IO]yD@AOU|D@gO]
