OL,3,CJustin Welby says he forgives abuser
OL,4,CSmyth and tells of 'personal failure'
OL,6,FAsked if he wanted forgiveness from
OL,7,FSmyth's victims, Mr Welby said:
OL,8,F"Obviously, but it's not about me.
OL,9,FWhen we talk about safeguarding, the
OL,10,Fcentre of it is the victims and
OL,11,Fsurvivors.
OL,13,F"I have never, ever said to a
OL,14,Fsurvivor, 'you must forgive', because
OL,15,Fthat is their sovereign, absolute
OL,16,Findividual choice. Everyone wants to
OL,17,Fbe forgiven, but to demand forgiveness
OL,18,Fis to abuse again."
