OL,3,CJustin Welby says he forgives abuser
OL,4,CSmyth and tells of 'personal failure'
OL,6,FRepeating an apology to abuse victims,
OL,7,Fhe said: "Just for the avoidance of
OL,8,Fdoubt, I am utterly sorry and feel a
OL,9,Fdeep sense of personal failure both
OL,10,Ffor the victims of Smyth not being
OL,11,Fpicked up sufficiently after 2017 when
OL,12,Fwe knew the extent of it, and for my
OL,13,Fown personal failures."
